---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Health & Safety | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="Health and safety at Surrey Contracting, CHAS accredited, full RAMS, site inductions, and audit-grade paperwork on every project."
  path="/health-safety"
  active="health-safety"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>Health &amp; Safety</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="page-title">Health &amp; Safety</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">Safety is our number one priority. Every project, every shift, every member of the team.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container hs-intro">
    <div class="hs-intro-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-yellow">Safety first</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Safety is our number one priority.</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">At Surrey Contracting, health and safety is such an important element of what we do. This is why we are always working hard to find new ways to improve our policies and systems, backed up by our project-specific risk assessments and method statements that are continuously monitored and updated.</p>
      <p>We are constantly rolling out training courses for our team, including First Aid at Work and new safety training, so our team can always be up to date on current policies and procedures.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow">Speak to our team →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hs-intro-visual">
      <img src="/assets/img/safety-first.png" alt="Safety First, construction worker wearing helmet, ear defenders and mask" class="hs-image">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section page-section-grey">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">How we deliver it</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Four pillars of safe delivery.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="hs-pillars">
      <article>
        <div class="hs-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Project-specific RAMS</h3>
        <p>Risk assessments and method statements written for the job, not pulled from a template. Reviewed weekly while works are live.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <div class="hs-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M3 12l3 3 6-6 6 6 3-3"/><path d="M3 18l3 3 6-6 6 6 3-3"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Continuous training</h3>
        <p>First Aid at Work, CSCS, CPCS / NPORS, asbestos awareness and SMSTS rolled out across the team on an ongoing basis.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <div class="hs-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Daily site checks</h3>
        <p>Plant pre-use, scaffold and excavation checks recorded daily. Toolbox talks delivered by the supervisor on the ground.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <div class="hs-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M4 4h16v12H5.5L4 18z"/><path d="M8 9h8M8 12h5"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Open reporting</h3>
        <p>Near-misses and observations logged and reviewed by management. We learn from incidents the industry would rather hide.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="accs">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="accs-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Accreditations &amp; memberships</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Audited. Verified. On the record.</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="acc-marquee" aria-label="Accreditation logos">
    <div class="acc-track">
      <div class="acc-set">
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/chas.webp" alt="CHAS"></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/safe-contractor.webp" alt="SafeContractor"></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/ssip.webp" alt="SSIP"></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/smas.webp" alt="SMAS"></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/citb.webp" alt="CITB"></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/cscs.webp" alt="CSCS"></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/npors.webp" alt="NPORS"></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/ipaf.webp" alt="IPAF"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-set" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/chas.webp" alt=""></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/safe-contractor.webp" alt=""></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/ssip.webp" alt=""></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/smas.webp" alt=""></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/citb.webp" alt=""></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/cscs.webp" alt=""></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/npors.webp" alt=""></div>
        <div class="acc-badge"><img src="/assets/acc/ipaf.webp" alt=""></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip" style="padding: 30px 0px;">
  <div class="container cta-strip-row">
    <div>
      <h3>Need a contractor that takes safety as seriously as you do?</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Talk to our team about pre-qualification, RAMS and accreditation packs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-strip-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow">Get in touch</a>
      <a href="tel:01932932650" class="btn btn-ghost-light">01932 932650</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
